@startuml

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign direction
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
autonumber

actor Voter
entity VotingApplication as "Voting Application"
entity DigitalBallotBox as "Digital Ballot Box"
database PublicBulletinBoard as "Public Bulletin Board"

Voter -> VotingApplication: Cast the most recently\nsubmitted ballot\n(with tracker S)
VotingApplication -> DigitalBallotBox: Cast request for\nsubmission tracker S
DigitalBallotBox -> PublicBulletinBoard: Request submission for S
PublicBulletinBoard --> DigitalBallotBox: Submission for S
DigitalBallotBox -> PublicBulletinBoard: Publish voter authorization
PublicBulletinBoard --> DigitalBallotBox: Tracker (VA) for published\nvoter authorization
DigitalBallotBox -> PublicBulletinBoard: Publish cast request for S
PublicBulletinBoard --> DigitalBallotBox: Tracker (C) for published\ncast request for S
DigitalBallotBox --> VotingApplication: Trackers C and S
Voter <-- VotingApplication: Present confirmation that casting is complete

@enduml
